item.title: The Fall of Mankind
item.description: Father: Walking Up the Mountain # The world is a closeted place, eyes watching, dogs barking. I am ever-present. I am a sinless guile. Run. Through. Send. Boo. Dancing tulips in a maiden’s garden. I shine once more unto the end. Unto the end. Sicamore tree eleven thresen basun tasun loon dogma randuin biffiesutenalupa.
